<li id="cite_note-44"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-44">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFMcBeanRodgers2010" class="citation journal cs1">McBean, Gordon; Rodgers, Caroline (2010). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wires.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/wcc.77">"Climate hazards and disasters: the need for capacity building"</a>. <i>WIREs Climate Change</i>. <b>1</b> (6): 871–884. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1002%2Fwcc.77">10.1002/wcc.77</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/1757-7780">1757-7780</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=WIREs+Climate+Change&amp;rft.atitle=Climate+hazards+and+disasters%3A+the+need+for+capacity+building&amp;rft.volume=1&amp;rft.issue=6&amp;rft.pages=871-884&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1002%2Fwcc.77&amp;rft.issn=1757-7780&amp;rft.aulast=McBean&amp;rft.aufirst=Gordon&amp;rft.au=Rodgers%2C+Caroline&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwires.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1002%2Fwcc.77&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AClimate+resilience" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
</ol></div>
